        "description": "Initial setup currently only works reliably in a desktop browser. On iPhone or Android, the installed MyBuderus app can intercept the final app redirect.\n\n1. Open the browser developer tools with F12 before logging in.\n2. Go to the Network tab and enable Preserve log.\n3. Open the SingleKey login URL below and sign in.\n4. After login, a network or redirect error page may appear. That is expected.\n5. In the Network tab, find the last `/auth/connect/authorize/callback` entry.\n6. Copy the `Location` response header. The URL starts with `com.buderus.tt.dashtt://app/login`.\n7. Paste that URL here.\n\n{authorization_url}",
